    "We present the full inference method of ENMA for latent generation in the pseudo-code 1:",
    "Algorithm 1: ENMA Inference: Autoregressive Latent Generation with Cosine Masked Decoding",
    "Encoding irregular spatio-temporal data into a compact latent representation is a central component of ENMA.",
    "Inspired by recent advances in vision models (Yu et al., 2023), ENMA combines two key elements.",
    "(i) a cross-attention module performs spatial interpolation, mapping the irregular inputs u 0:L-1 (X), defined over an arbitrary spatial grid X at L time steps, onto a regular grid Ξ, yielding intermediate representations u 0:L-1 (Ξ)."
